Project Structure

panther_hotel/
    app.py
Flask backend & API routes
    requirements.txt
    templates/
        base.html
Shared layout (nav and footer)
    index.html
/ landing page
    rooms.html
Room listings & booking page
    static/
        css/main.css
styles
    js/main.js

Setup and run
1.    pip install -r requirements.txt
2.  run the dev server
        python app.py
3. Open in browser
    https://localhost:5000
